author: The Current
description:
Watch Beach Weather perform an acoustic version of "Sex, Drugs, Etc."
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

While in town for a concert at the Armory in Minneapolis, the Boston-originated indie-rock band Beach Weather visited The Current studio for a session hosted by Mac Wilson. Dipping into their catalogue, Beach Weather performed an acoustic set of songs. Watch and listen to a performance of "Sex, Drugs, Etc." above.

Musicians
Nick Santino – vocals, guitar
Reeve Powers – bass, vocals
Sean Silverman – guitar, vocals
